          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>charred pepper, bean & cheese quesadillas </strong>to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Place a second baking tray on top to weigh them down slightly</p><p>Put the <strong>stacked baking trays</strong> in the oven for 12 min or until the quesadillas are slightly browned and the cheese is melted</p>",
